野, 投資文件,CERT, 稅單"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T08:29:05.000Z","msg":"我屋企都係近海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，除霉劑我都有用，廁所果d黑邊同洗衣機入面果d黑跡都有用。<br />\n<br />\n仲有用日本納米清潔海綿，自從用左佢，易清好多，個腥盤少左好多老泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n想問下5係咩黎？我屋企都有窗紗，好多塵。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T08:45:31.000Z","msg":"專門擦窗紗嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我發現就算用抹布都唔夠用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留段片解釋你聽<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EeY5T4q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEeY5T4q.png&h=a5d2ed36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9ajfEjybMas\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9ajfEjybMas&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3LTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=b9fe9b5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9ajfEjybMas</a>"},{"pid":"c45f6aee6325bae430a1453c702e833f2320dd43","tid":1792932,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e97d54950488a391044186008e3087b693ce21e7","tid":1792932,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13d5d20fc3f6daad7bf9b412412a6dbf8f4f4bc9","tid":1792932,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa90e3fb3479a9699fee97fd0b0c2d66cc958cab","tid":1792932,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T08:22:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T08:36:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我指以前屋企鋪牆紙，住左20年。宜家邊邊飛晒出來，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n補牆真係好正，少少裂紋個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T08:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\